    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es turru Meern/ bet kad\nes runnaju/ tad tee Kildu pa-\njett."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta CXXI. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Eepreezinfschanas Dseefma/ ka tee/\njas us Deewu ween ferre: 1/ 2. Preeksch"
